trans-unit.source: Provides a user interface for selecting a message queue path.
trans-unit.target: Gir et brukergrensesnitt for å velge en message queue-bane.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Messaging.Design.QueuePathEditor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Messaging.Design.QueuePathEditor"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Edits the value of the specified message queue using the specified type descriptor context and service provider.
trans-unit.target: Redigerer verdien for den angitte meldingskøen ved hjelp av angitt type sikkerhetsbeskrivelse konteksten og tjenesten leverandøren.

trans-unit.source: If `value` is not a <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue> or a string that specifies a message queue path, this method returns `value`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis `value` er ikke en <xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue>eller en streng som angir en message queue-bane, denne metoden returnerer `value`.</xref:System.Messaging.MessageQueue>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, this method returns the new message queue path.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden, ellers returneres den nye message queue banen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that provides additional context information.
A <xref:System.IServiceProvider> that the editor can use to obtain services.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.IServiceProvider>at redigeringsprogrammet kan bruke til å hente services.</xref:System.IServiceProvider>

trans-unit.source: The new value of the message queue path.
trans-unit.target: Den nye verdien av message queue banen.

trans-unit.source: Returns the editing style used by the <xref:System.Messaging.Design.QueuePathEditor.EditValue*> method.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer redigering som brukes av den <xref:System.Messaging.Design.QueuePathEditor.EditValue*>metoden.</xref:System.Messaging.Design.QueuePathEditor.EditValue*>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that provides additional context information.
